Dialogue: 3,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}几乎算不上机构经纪人
Dialogue: 2,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.06,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hardly an institutional broker
Dialogue: 3,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}UTI 还没有给我们任何业务
Dialogue: 2,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}UTI still hasnt given us any business
Dialogue: 3,0:05:14.94,0:05:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我已经厌倦了这种15% 的游戏
Dialogue: 2,0:05:14.94,0:05:16.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And Im tired of this 15 per cent game
Dialogue: 3,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}机构有这么多钱，却没有计划
Dialogue: 2,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Institutions have so much money but no plan
Dialogue: 3,0:05:22.18,0:05:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}老实说，如果我有那么多钱
Dialogue: 2,0:05:22.18,0:05:23.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}To be honest, if I had that kind of money
Dialogue: 3,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}指数会上涨4000点
Dialogue: 2,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}the market would have been up by 4,000 points
Dialogue: 3,0:05:26.34,0:05:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那就拿去吧，这是你的钱，拿去投资吧
Dialogue: 2,0:05:26.34,0:05:29.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then take it up Its your money, go on and invest it
Dialogue: 3,0:05:29.66,0:05:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说什么来着? 风险是生活的调味品 ，对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.66,0:05:32.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Whats that you say? Risk is the spice of life, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}亲爱的，威士忌也很危险
Dialogue: 2,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Darling, whiskey is risky too
Dialogue: 3,0:05:36.26,0:05:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要不你也尝尝这个，来吧
Dialogue: 2,0:05:36.26,0:05:38.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have a taste of this spice too Come on
Dialogue: 3,0:05:38.62,0:05:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你真是不可理喻
Dialogue: 2,0:05:38.62,0:05:40.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You are impossible
Dialogue: 3,0:05:42.58,0:05:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘿，普拉纳夫 · 谢斯，你的笑声在一英里以外都能听到
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.58,0:05:45.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hey, Pranav Sheth, your laughter can be heard from a mile away
Dialogue: 3,0:05:46.02,0:05:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿贾伊大哥！
Dialogue: 2,0:05:46.02,0:05:47.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ajay Bhai!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:47.70,0:05:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太好了，我很高兴你离我只有一英里远
Dialogue: 2,0:05:47.70,0:05:51.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Wonderful Im glad you were just a mile away
Dialogue: 3,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为我的笑声传不到加尔各答
Dialogue: 2,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}coz my laughter cant reach all the way to Calcutta
Dialogue: 3,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 干杯-干杯
Dialogue: 2,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Cheers! - Cheers
Dialogue: 3,0:05:56.74,0:05:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 普拉那夫! -什么事？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:56.74,0:05:59.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Man] Pranav! - Yes?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:00.02,0:06:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不能喝酒，但是你可以拿着它，对吧? 给你
Dialogue: 2,0:06:00.02,0:06:04.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You cant drink, but you can hold it, right? Here
Dialogue: 3,0:06:04.18,0:06:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去吧，表达你的敬意，大个子
Dialogue: 2,0:06:04.18,0:06:06.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go on, pay your respects Big man
Dialogue: 3,0:06:06.94,0:06:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}呆在这儿别动
Dialogue: 2,0:06:06.94,0:06:07.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Stay right here
Dialogue: 3,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘿，你好吗? 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pranav] Hey, howre you?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:12.98,0:06:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿贾伊大哥，我是哈尔沙德
Dialogue: 2,0:06:12.98,0:06:15.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ajay Bhai, Harshad
Dialogue: 3,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-哈尔沙德 · 梅塔 -阿贾伊 · 凯迪亚，干杯
Dialogue: 2,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Harshad Mehta - Ajay Kedia Cheers
Dialogue: 3,0:06:18.38,0:06:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哦不，这是普拉那夫的酒
Dialogue: 2,0:06:18.38,0:06:19.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh no no This is Pranav Bhais
Dialogue: 3,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不喝酒，顺便说一下，我听说过很多关于你的事
Dialogue: 2,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I dont drink By the way, Ive heard a lot about you
Dialogue: 3,0:06:24.42,0:06:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}自从我进入这个市场，我就听说了加尔各答的凯迪亚先生
Dialogue: 2,0:06:24.42,0:06:27.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ever since Ive entered the market, Ive heard of Mr Kedia from Calcutta
Dialogue: 3,0:06:29.42,0:06:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}1982年的黑色星期四，股市崩盘 ？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:29.42,0:06:33.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That Black Thursday crash of 1982?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:33.66,0:06:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你和信实股份的 ？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:33.66,0:06:34.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}yours and Reliances?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:35.74,0:06:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那天我也损失了十万卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:06:35.74,0:06:38.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I too lost lakhs that day
Dialogue: 3,0:06:40.02,0:06:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的意思是，我那时正要从市场上卷铺盖走人
Dialogue: 2,0:06:40.02,0:06:44.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, I was on the verge of packing up from the market Bag and baggage
Dialogue: 3,0:06:47.22,0:06:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈里什，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:47.22,0:06:48.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harish, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:48.42,0:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 哈尔沙德，哈尔沙德・梅塔-哦对，哈尔沙德
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.42,0:06:51.06,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Harshad Harshad Mehta - Yes, Harshad
Dialogue: 3,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给你一句忠告，哈沙德
Dialogue: 2,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A word of advice for you Harshad
Dialogue: 3,0:06:55.22,0:06:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你承受不了这么大的压力，就趁早走人，好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.22,0:06:58.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you cant take the heat, get out of the kitchen Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:59.34,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是那样的
Dialogue: 2,0:06:59.34,0:07:00.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Its not like that
Dialogue: 3,0:07:00.66,0:07:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们结束了你的股市生涯，我真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 2,0:07:00.66,0:07:05.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And Im really sorry if we ended your stint in the market
Dialogue: 3,0:07:06.10,0:07:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 嗯? 非常抱歉-不不
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.10,0:07:08.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hmmm? Very sorry about that - No, no
Dialogue: 3,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事实上，我现在已经开始做咨询工作了
Dialogue: 2,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In fact, Ive started my own consultancy now
Dialogue: 3,0:07:10.82,0:07:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你的?-是的
Dialogue: 2,0:07:10.82,0:07:11.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Yours? - Yes
Dialogue: 3,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}高摩投资
Dialogue: 2,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.06,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Growmore
Dialogue: 3,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，高摩先生
Dialogue: 2,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Alright, Mr Growmore
Dialogue: 3,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}回头见
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I will see you around
Dialogue: 3,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你能留在市场上
Dialogue: 2,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}if you stay around
Dialogue: 3,0:07:35.94,0:07:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}过来
Dialogue: 2,0:07:35.94,0:07:37.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come here
Dialogue: 3,0:07:57.46,0:07:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生，我的饮料呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:57.46,0:07:59.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh, Mr Mehta? Wheres my drink?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:00.90,0:08:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的天！
Dialogue: 2,0:08:00.90,0:08:02.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bloody hell!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:03.90,0:08:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你把我的酒喝完了？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:03.90,0:08:04.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You finished my drink?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个凯迪亚到底是谁？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who the hell is this Kedia?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他的态度是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Whats with his attitude?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他当然有自己的态度
Dialogue: 2,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Of course he has an attitude
Dialogue: 3,0:08:16.62,0:08:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他实际上拥有股票市场，他来自一个商人家庭
Dialogue: 2,0:08:16.62,0:08:20.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He practically owns the share market He comes from a family of traders
Dialogue: 3,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他同时管理着四家公司
Dialogue: 2,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He manages four companies simultaneously
Dialogue: 3,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一只脚在货币市场，另一只脚在股票市场
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}One foot in the money market and the other in the share market
Dialogue: 3,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}政府债券、 PSU 债券  规模巨大
Dialogue: 2,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pranav] Government securities, PSU bonds At a huge scale 
Dialogue: 3,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}货币市场？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Money market?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}政府债券有这么多钱可以赚吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is there so much money to be made in government securities?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那是财富的集市，兄弟！
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Its the bazaar of wealth, brother!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:38.26,0:08:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我一件事，我们的股票市场每天的成交量是多少？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.26,0:08:43.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay, tell me one thing What is the daily volume of our share market?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:45.22,0:08:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大约一千亿卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.22,0:08:46.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Around 10,000 crores
Dialogue: 3,0:08:47.86,0:08:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}猜猜货币市场每天的成交量是多少? 两万亿卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:08:47.86,0:08:51.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And guess the daily volume of the money market? Two lakh crores
Dialogue: 3,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此，态度
Dialogue: 2,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Therefore, attitude
Dialogue: 3,0:09:07.42,0:09:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿什温，你见过板球运动员打网球吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:07.42,0:09:11.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ashwin, have you ever seen a cricketer play tennis?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:12.22,0:09:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使在网球场上，也有草地球场、红土球场  而且每个球场的比赛都不同
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.22,0:09:16.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But even in tennis, there is a grass court, a clay court and the game is different for each
Dialogue: 3,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这种货币市场游戏超出了你的能力
Dialogue: 2,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This money market game is out of your league
Dialogue: 3,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，这六个月来一切都很顺利
Dialogue: 2,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] Harshad, its all been going well for six months
Dialogue: 3,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 为什么这么着迷?-什么进展顺利？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Now why this new obsession? - Whats been going well?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:25.98,0:09:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}高摩只是我们的公司名字，增长在哪里？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.98,0:09:27.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Growmore is just our name, wheres the growth?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:29.22,0:09:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}机构经纪业务还不够好
Dialogue: 2,0:09:29.22,0:09:31.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Institutional broking is not good enough
Dialogue: 3,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们必须想出一些新的东西
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have to think of something new
Dialogue: 3,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}业务达到饱和点，而不是大脑，或者说我们也应该让大脑饱和了？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Businesses reach saturation points, not brains Or do we stop using our brains as well?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:37.46,0:09:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我明白了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:37.46,0:09:38.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I get it
Dialogue: 3,0:09:39.42,0:09:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那个阿贾伊 · 凯迪亚，他吓到你了，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:39.42,0:09:41.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That Ajay Kedia, hes rattled you, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，你现在是在给我们上课
Dialogue: 2,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pranav] And so, youre lecturing us now
Dialogue: 3,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为什么不说清楚点
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why dont you speak clearly
Dialogue: 3,0:09:46.26,0:09:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为他对你态度不好，你就要搞他吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:46.26,0:09:51.06,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that you want to stick a finger up his, for the way he treated you?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:52.30,0:09:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里有人知道货币市场是什么吗
Dialogue: 2,0:09:52.30,0:09:55.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] Does anyone here even know what the money market is?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你有什么可靠的计划吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you have any solid plan in mind?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这才是正确的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now thats the right question
Dialogue: 3,0:10:01.54,0:10:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看，股票市场和货币市场并没有很大的不同
Dialogue: 2,0:10:01.54,0:10:03.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, the share market and money market arent very different
Dialogue: 3,0:10:04.98,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在这里，我们交易的不是股票，而是
Dialogue: 2,0:10:04.98,0:10:07.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Here, instead of shares, we trade in
Dialogue: 3,0:10:07.70,0:10:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)} 政府证券，PSU 债券和单位
Dialogue: 2,0:10:07.70,0:10:09.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}government securities, PSU bonds and units
Dialogue: 3,0:10:10.22,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们都知道经纪人了解公司股票的价值
Dialogue: 2,0:10:10.22,0:10:12.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We all know that a broker understands a companys shares value
Dialogue: 3,0:10:12.54,0:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}比公司更了解，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:10:12.54,0:10:13.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}better than the company itself, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:13.58,0:10:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的
Dialogue: 2,0:10:13.58,0:10:14.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes
Dialogue: 3,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}同样，在货币市场 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Similarly, in the money market
Dialogue: 3,0:10:16.26,0:10:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)} 哪些银行想要购买有价证券，以及他们从哪里可以得到这些证券
Dialogue: 2,0:10:16.26,0:10:19.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}which banks want to buy securities and where they can get them
Dialogue: 3,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}消息来源都是经纪人
Dialogue: 2,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}is in the brokers knowledge
Dialogue: 3,0:10:22.26,0:10:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们的工作是同时管理需求和供应
Dialogue: 2,0:10:22.26,0:10:24.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] Our job is to manage both demand and supply
Dialogue: 3,0:10:24.74,0:10:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每笔货币市场交易中最重要的文件就是SGL
Dialogue: 2,0:10:24.74,0:10:29.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The most important document in every money market transaction is the SGL note
Dialogue: 3,0:10:31.22,0:10:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SGL 是指明细总帐
Dialogue: 2,0:10:31.22,0:10:33.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SGL means Subsidiary General Ledger
Dialogue: 3,0:10:33.70,0:10:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[阿什温]现在让我们假设，我从你那里买了1000手
Dialogue: 2,0:10:33.70,0:10:36.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] Now lets assume, I buy 1000 units from you
Dialogue: 3,0:10:36.78,0:10:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，你给我一张 SGL 的票据作为回报
Dialogue: 2,0:10:36.78,0:10:39.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, you give me an SGL note in return
Dialogue: 3,0:10:39.86,0:10:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我把这个 SGL 存在 PDO 里 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:39.86,0:10:43.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I deposit this SGL in the PDO
Dialogue: 3,0:10:43.22,0:10:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}PDO是印度储备银行的公共债务办公室
Dialogue: 2,0:10:43.22,0:10:45.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that is Public Debt Office of the RBI
Dialogue: 3,0:10:45.74,0:10:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)} PDO 拥有你所有债券的交易记录
Dialogue: 2,0:10:45.74,0:10:48.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The PDO holds the account for all your units
Dialogue: 3,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}经纪人、银行  每个人都希望自己的业务快速增长
Dialogue: 2,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] Brokers, banks everyone wants their business to grow fast
Dialogue: 3,0:10:51.90,0:10:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们说，SGLs 减慢了交易速度
Dialogue: 2,0:10:51.90,0:10:55.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And they say, SGLs slow down transactions
Dialogue: 3,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此，我们将使用 BR 代替 SGL
Dialogue: 2,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, instead of SGL, we will use BR
Dialogue: 3,0:10:59.46,0:11:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- ‘ BR 意思是银行收据-‘ Hmm 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:59.46,0:11:02.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Bhushan] BR meaning Bank Receipt -[Rebello] Hmm
Dialogue: 3,0:11:02.50,0:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这意味着，即使没有SGL，交易也是可以进行的
Dialogue: 2,0:11:02.50,0:11:06.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That means transactions are now possible without SGL
Dialogue: 3,0:11:06.30,0:11:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不需要中央权威
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.30,0:11:07.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There is no central authority
Dialogue: 3,0:11:08.18,0:11:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在，当一家银行想把自己的证券卖给另一家银行时 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:08.18,0:11:11.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, when one bank wants to sell its securities to another
Dialogue: 3,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)} 他们可以简单地开一张收据 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}they can simply issue a receipt
Dialogue: 3,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}  保证他们有证券
Dialogue: 2,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}guaranteeing that they have the securities
Dialogue: 3,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们在花旗银行有联系人吗
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] Do we have a contact in Citibank?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:30.10,0:11:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们没有，但我已经安排了和 K · S · 特亚吉的会面  
Dialogue: 2,0:11:30.10,0:11:32.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] We dont have a contact but Ive fixed a meeting with K S Tyagi
Dialogue: 3,0:11:32.98,0:11:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)} 他处理所有的货币市场交易 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:32.98,0:11:35.06,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}he handles all their money market deals
Dialogue: 3,0:11:35.22,0:11:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他在市场上被称为八木（印度板球运动员）
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.22,0:11:36.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hes known as Tyagu in the market
Dialogue: 3,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生，你有没有能力并不重要
Dialogue: 2,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr Mehta, its not important whether youre capable or not
Dialogue: 3,0:11:39.98,0:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}重要的是你是否了解这个市场
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.98,0:11:42.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What is important is whether you understand this market
Dialogue: 3,0:11:43.54,0:11:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}首先，了解这个市场，然后我们再谈
Dialogue: 2,0:11:43.54,0:11:46.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}First, learn about this market and then approach us
Dialogue: 3,0:11:47.22,0:11:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那我们走着瞧吧
Dialogue: 2,0:11:47.22,0:11:48.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then well see
Dialogue: 3,0:11:49.74,0:11:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是说，因为我们是局外人，你就不和我们做生意？
Dialogue: 2,0:11:49.74,0:11:53.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You mean to say, you wont do business with us because we are outsiders?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不是局内人或局外人的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Its not a question of insider or outsider
Dialogue: 3,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我已经有了我现有的经纪人
Dialogue: 2,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I already have my existing set of brokers
Dialogue: 3,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么我要和新人一起工作？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why should I work with somebody new?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，曾经有一段时间，我在股票市场也是新手
Dialogue: 2,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.06,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, there was a time, I was new at the stock markets too
Dialogue: 3,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我走出了自己的路
Dialogue: 2,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I found my way through it
Dialogue: 3,0:12:10.02,0:12:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此，我相信我也可以在货币市场上做到这一点
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.02,0:12:11.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, I am sure I can do it with money markets too
Dialogue: 3,0:12:16.02,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生，让我给你一些建议
Dialogue: 2,0:12:16.02,0:12:18.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr Mehta, let me give you some very good advice
Dialogue: 3,0:12:19.90,0:12:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是货币市场
Dialogue: 2,0:12:19.90,0:12:20.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the money market
Dialogue: 3,0:12:22.18,0:12:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来自股票市场的顶级经纪人想要进入这个市场，是不可能的
Dialogue: 2,0:12:22.18,0:12:25.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Top brokers from the stock market want to enter it, but they cant
Dialogue: 3,0:12:28.78,0:12:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道为什么吗? 因为血统
Dialogue: 2,0:12:28.78,0:12:31.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You know why? Because of pedigree
Dialogue: 3,0:12:32.26,0:12:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}血统在这里非常重要
Dialogue: 2,0:12:32.26,0:12:33.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pedigree is very important here
Dialogue: 3,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Tyagi ]这个市场没有新人的位置
Dialogue: 2,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Tyagi] Theres no place for new people in this market
Dialogue: 3,0:12:38.46,0:12:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你也不应该尝试
Dialogue: 2,0:12:38.46,0:12:40.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You shouldnt try either
Dialogue: 3,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢你的建议，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thank you for your advice, sir
Dialogue: 3,0:12:48.10,0:12:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我不确定这个建议对你还是对我有利
Dialogue: 2,0:12:48.10,0:12:50.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I am not sure if it was in my interest or yours
Dialogue: 3,0:12:53.82,0:12:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}祝你今天过得愉快
Dialogue: 2,0:12:53.82,0:12:54.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have a good day
