Dialogue: 2,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Whos that?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:11.74,0:13:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿贾伊 · 凯迪亚
Dialogue: 2,0:13:11.74,0:13:12.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ajay Kedia
Dialogue: 3,0:13:19.78,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.78,0:13:20.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay
Dialogue: 3,0:13:24.90,0:13:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗨
Dialogue: 2,0:13:24.90,0:13:25.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hi
Dialogue: 3,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 等一下-抱歉打扰了
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Just a second - I am sorry to interrupt you
Dialogue: 3,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没关系
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thats okay
Dialogue: 3,0:13:29.18,0:13:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能见见你们的财政部长内拉吉·乔普拉先生吗？
