Dialogue: 3,0:13:31.46,0:13:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你今天和他有预约吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.46,0:13:33.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Did you have an appointment with him today?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉他是哈尔沙德·梅塔
Dialogue: 2,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just tell him its Harshad Mehta
Dialogue: 3,0:13:37.30,0:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯  对不起，先生，他现在不在
Dialogue: 2,0:13:37.30,0:13:40.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Uhm Sorry, sir, but he is not available
Dialogue: 3,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你能给我预约一个明天见他的时间吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can you give me an appointment with him for tomorrow?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，恐怕他明天就要去马德拉斯了
Dialogue: 2,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, Im afraid but hes leaving for Madras tomorrow
Dialogue: 3,0:13:45.78,0:13:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他要离开一段时间
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.78,0:13:47.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He will be out of station for a while
