Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.70,0:15:01.06,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Niraj] Look, Harshad, right? - Yeah
Dialogue: 3,0:15:02.46,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}花旗银行是这片丛林的王者
Dialogue: 2,0:15:02.46,0:15:04.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Citibank is the king of this jungle
