Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Theyve made the whole money market into an exclusive club
Dialogue: 3,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们不喜欢外人
Dialogue: 2,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And they do not like outsiders
Dialogue: 3,0:15:13.94,0:15:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天，货币市场就像是一家银行及其经纪人的领地
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.94,0:15:17.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Today, the money market feels like the territory of one bank and its brokers
Dialogue: 3,0:15:18.46,0:15:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是个该死的垄断集团
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.46,0:15:19.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Its a goddamn cartel
Dialogue: 3,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而八木就是集团的老大
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And Tyagi, hes the boss of this cartel
Dialogue: 3,0:15:25.58,0:15:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他的经纪人，阿贾伊·凯迪亚，Hiten Shroff，哈曼德拉·卡帕迪亚
