Dialogue: 2,0:16:01.02,0:16:01.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, I get it
Dialogue: 3,0:16:03.34,0:16:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}花旗银行与八木和他的经纪人有自己的集团
Dialogue: 2,0:16:03.34,0:16:06.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Citibank has its own cartel with Tyagi and his brokers
Dialogue: 3,0:16:07.42,0:16:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，为什么我们不能建立自己的集团来对抗他们呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:07.42,0:16:09.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, why cant we form our own cartel against them?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:10.50,0:16:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，我是认真的
Dialogue: 2,0:16:10.50,0:16:11.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, Im serious
Dialogue: 3,0:16:12.38,0:16:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}老实告诉我，你从来没有想过这个吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:12.38,0:16:15.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell me honestly, Niraj Bhai Have you never thought of this?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然想过，事实上经常想
Dialogue: 2,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Of course, I have Often, in fact
Dialogue: 3,0:16:19.46,0:16:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就像这样，我也有很多其他的幻想
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.46,0:16:21.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And like this, I have many other fantasies too
Dialogue: 3,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我们有武德
Dialogue: 2,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But we also have ethics
Dialogue: 3,0:16:24.86,0:16:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}八木和他的团伙不讲武德
Dialogue: 2,0:16:24.86,0:16:28.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tyagi and his cartel know no ethics
Dialogue: 3,0:16:29.54,0:16:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不能像他们那样做肮脏的交易
Dialogue: 2,0:16:29.54,0:16:31.34,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We cant do dirty business like them
Dialogue: 3,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我明白，你不应该做肮脏的生意
Dialogue: 2,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I understand You should never do dirty business
Dialogue: 3,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我可以，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I can, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你觉得
Dialogue: 2,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you think
Dialogue: 3,0:16:41.62,0:16:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}八木真的知道他的经纪人是怎么给他拉生意的？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:41.62,0:16:45.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tyagi really knows how his brokers bring him business?
