Dialogue: 2,0:16:46.74,0:16:47.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes and no
Dialogue: 3,0:16:50.10,0:16:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以同样的，你不需要知道我是如何帮你得到这笔生意的
Dialogue: 2,0:16:50.10,0:16:53.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So similarly, you dont need to know how I get you the business
