Dialogue: 2,0:16:53.62,0:16:56.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You show the path Just tell me where to start
Dialogue: 3,0:16:56.94,0:16:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的时间，我的努力
Dialogue: 2,0:16:56.94,0:16:59.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My time, my effort
