Dialogue: 2,0:17:08.70,0:17:10.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You knew I was going to be on this flight, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:12.78,0:17:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是也不是
Dialogue: 2,0:17:12.78,0:17:13.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes and no
Dialogue: 3,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}集团的成功离不开优秀的人才
Dialogue: 2,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A cartel is as good as its members
Dialogue: 3,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们今天要见的人
