Dialogue: 3,0:17:19.62,0:17:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是你们集团的潜在成员
Dialogue: 2,0:17:19.62,0:17:21.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hes a potential member to your cartel
Dialogue: 3,0:17:22.98,0:17:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们的集团
Dialogue: 2,0:17:22.98,0:17:23.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Our cartel
Dialogue: 3,0:17:25.46,0:17:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的集团
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.46,0:17:26.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your cartel
Dialogue: 3,0:17:26.54,0:17:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我在 Grindlays 有很多熟人
