Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.46,0:17:31.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Its confirmed that
Dialogue: 3,0:17:32.14,0:17:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Grindlays 在寻找货币市场经纪人
Dialogue: 2,0:17:32.14,0:17:34.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Grindlays is on the look-out for money market brokers
Dialogue: 3,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们不想要花旗银行集团的任何人
Dialogue: 2,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And they dont want anyone from the Citibank cartel
Dialogue: 3,0:17:41.22,0:17:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这一切都没问题，但最大的问题是花旗银行(Citibank)
Dialogue: 2,0:17:41.22,0:17:44.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All that is fine, but the biggest problem is, Citibank
Dialogue: 3,0:17:44.38,0:17:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们有足够的资金购买这些证券
Dialogue: 2,0:17:44.38,0:17:46.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They have all the funds to buy the securities
Dialogue: 3,0:17:47.58,0:17:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦他们垄断市场，他们的经纪人就可以操纵一切
Dialogue: 2,0:17:47.58,0:17:52.06,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once they corner the market, their brokers manipulate everything
Dialogue: 3,0:17:52.58,0:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看来你不看电视
Dialogue: 2,0:17:52.58,0:17:54.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Seems like you dont watch TV
