Dialogue: 2,0:17:56.26,0:17:56.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Of course
Dialogue: 3,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，你没看到
