Dialogue: 3,0:18:01.54,0:18:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}解决办法就在于此
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.54,0:18:02.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The solution lies within that
