Dialogue: 2,0:18:03.66,0:18:04.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:04.86,0:18:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，花旗银行扔的是鸟食
Dialogue: 2,0:18:04.86,0:18:06.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, Citibank throws birdseed
Dialogue: 3,0:18:06.90,0:18:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每家银行都开始啄它，太孤立了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:06.90,0:18:09.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And like a sparrow, every bank begins pecking on it, that too alone
Dialogue: 3,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此，很容易陷入困境
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And so, its easy to get trapped
Dialogue: 3,0:18:14.18,0:18:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你想说什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.18,0:18:15.34,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And whats your point?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是想说，现在是所有银行团结起来的时候了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The point is, its time for all banks to come together
Dialogue: 3,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}像这样，我们是一体的
Dialogue: 2,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Like this We are one
Dialogue: 3,0:18:20.90,0:18:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们很坚强，我们很勇敢
Dialogue: 2,0:18:20.90,0:18:23.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are strong We are courageous
Dialogue: 3,0:18:23.38,0:18:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦我们团结起来，我们就能做大事
Dialogue: 2,0:18:23.38,0:18:25.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once we unite, we can achieve big things
Dialogue: 3,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不能和任何银行打交道
Dialogue: 2,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We just cant deal with any bank
Dialogue: 3,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们还必须考虑利润和损失
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We also have to think about profit and loss
Dialogue: 3,0:18:29.94,0:18:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就这一次，拍打你的翅膀，和猎人的网一起飞走
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.94,0:18:32.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}For once, flap your wings together and fly off with the hunters net
Dialogue: 3,0:18:32.70,0:18:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}利润会随之而来
Dialogue: 2,0:18:32.70,0:18:33.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Profit will follow
