Dialogue: 3,0:23:16.34,0:23:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是指，所有的行动
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.34,0:23:17.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I mean, all actions
Dialogue: 3,0:23:18.90,0:23:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我需要他所有交易的详细情况
Dialogue: 2,0:23:18.90,0:23:20.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I need the details of all his transactions
Dialogue: 3,0:23:22.74,0:23:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不能在这件事上马马虎虎
Dialogue: 2,0:23:22.74,0:23:24.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We cant be caught napping on this
Dialogue: 3,0:23:25.18,0:23:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}绝对不能
Dialogue: 2,0:23:25.18,0:23:25.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No
Dialogue: 3,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说，我为什么要为这样一件小事请你来呢? 
Dialogue: 2,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pranav] I said, why would I take a favour from you for such a small matter?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:28.90,0:23:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我来找你要点大的东西
Dialogue: 2,0:23:28.90,0:23:30.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Id come to you for something big
Dialogue: 3,0:23:33.82,0:23:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我不要-嗯？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:33.82,0:23:35.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Not for me - Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:36.06,0:23:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一只脚踏进货币市场  你就放弃了糖果？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:36.06,0:23:37.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}One foot in the money market and youve given up sweets?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:37.90,0:23:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是放弃，而是控制
Dialogue: 2,0:23:37.90,0:23:39.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not given up just controlling
Dialogue: 3,0:23:39.82,0:23:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你什么时候开始控制自己的？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:39.82,0:23:41.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When did you start controlling yourself?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:43.22,0:23:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些日子，你不就是那个失控的人吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:43.22,0:23:45.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Well, these days, arent you the one whos out of control?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:46.26,0:23:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我已经看到你把 ACC 推得有多高 完全失控
Dialogue: 2,0:23:46.26,0:23:49.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ive seen how high youve pushed ACC out of control
Dialogue: 3,0:23:52.50,0:23:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还在密切关注市场动向？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:52.50,0:23:54.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Keeping tabs on the market, huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:55.98,0:23:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看来猎豹错过了他的丛林！
Dialogue: 2,0:23:55.98,0:23:57.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Looks like the cheetah is missing his jungle!
Dialogue: 3,0:23:58.98,0:24:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是现在的情况是，是时候抛弃 ACC 了
Dialogue: 2,0:23:58.98,0:24:01.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But the word is, its time to ditch ACC
Dialogue: 3,0:24:03.26,0:24:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}马努和他的手下正在摩拳擦掌
Dialogue: 2,0:24:03.26,0:24:04.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Manu Bhai and his men are targeting it
Dialogue: 3,0:24:05.34,0:24:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果他们开始做空，我就没有资金持有了
Dialogue: 2,0:24:05.34,0:24:08.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If they start shorting, I dont have the funds to hold on
Dialogue: 3,0:24:09.26,0:24:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是我们公牛的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:24:09.26,0:24:10.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the problem with us Bulls
Dialogue: 3,0:24:11.54,0:24:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当我们依赖市场获取资金的时候，那些看空者就会知道
Dialogue: 2,0:24:11.54,0:24:15.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The moment we depend on the market for funds, those bears get to know
Dialogue: 3,0:24:21.38,0:24:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}顺便问一下，你需要多少钱？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:21.38,0:24:22.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}By the way, how much do you need?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:28.74,0:24:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德说，现在是重返市场的最好时机
Dialogue: 2,0:24:28.74,0:24:30.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] This is the right time to get back into the market
Dialogue: 3,0:24:30.58,0:24:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然，谁阻止你了
Dialogue: 2,0:24:30.58,0:24:33.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] Sure Whos stopping you?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:33.74,0:24:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是不要去追求 ACC
Dialogue: 2,0:24:33.74,0:24:35.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But dont go after ACC
Dialogue: 3,0:24:36.70,0:24:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，如果普拉纳夫没有资金，我们也没有什么宝藏箱
Dialogue: 2,0:24:36.70,0:24:40.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, if Pranav doesnt have the funds, its not like we have a treasure chest
Dialogue: 3,0:24:42.90,0:24:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}卡纳拉银行想要购买一些证券，对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:42.90,0:24:44.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Canara Bank wanted to buy some securities, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:44.74,0:24:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们有寄支票来吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:44.74,0:24:45.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They were to send a cheque?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:47.02,0:24:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是这个
Dialogue: 2,0:24:47.02,0:24:48.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There it is
Dialogue: 3,0:24:50.62,0:24:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，我们应该从谁那里买债券呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:50.62,0:24:52.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, whom should we buy the bonds from?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:53.34,0:24:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Grindlays会有，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:53.34,0:24:54.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Grindlays will have, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:55.62,0:24:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦我们拿到收据，我会亲自把它们送到卡纳拉银行
Dialogue: 2,0:24:55.62,0:24:59.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once we get the BRs, Ill deliver them personally to Canara Bank
Dialogue: 3,0:24:59.98,0:25:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我已经有一段时间没去那儿了
Dialogue: 2,0:24:59.98,0:25:01.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Its been a while since Ive been there
Dialogue: 3,0:25:03.14,0:25:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们今天把这些支票全部存入我们的帐户
Dialogue: 2,0:25:03.14,0:25:05.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Lets deposit all these cheques into our account today
Dialogue: 3,0:25:05.86,0:25:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}卡纳拉银行需要十天后的证券
Dialogue: 2,0:25:05.86,0:25:07.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Canara Bank needs the securities after ten days
Dialogue: 3,0:25:09.42,0:25:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，你
Dialogue: 2,0:25:09.42,0:25:10.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, you
Dialogue: 3,0:25:11.66,0:25:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你疯了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:11.66,0:25:13.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 3,0:25:13.42,0:25:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不是我们的钱
Dialogue: 2,0:25:13.42,0:25:14.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is not our money
Dialogue: 3,0:25:15.90,0:25:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们想回到市场，这是我们的宝藏箱
Dialogue: 2,0:25:15.90,0:25:18.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If we want to get back in the market, this is our treasure chest
Dialogue: 3,0:25:19.62,0:25:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，这是个远期交易
Dialogue: 2,0:25:19.62,0:25:21.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, its a ready forward deal
Dialogue: 3,0:25:21.98,0:25:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦 BR 到期，我们就得把钱退回去
Dialogue: 2,0:25:21.98,0:25:25.34,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once the BR expires, well have to return the money
Dialogue: 3,0:25:25.42,0:25:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们会的，还有整整十天的时间
Dialogue: 2,0:25:25.42,0:25:27.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And we will We have ten whole days
Dialogue: 3,0:25:28.30,0:25:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在那之前，这些钱无论如何都会在我们的账户里慢慢消失
Dialogue: 2,0:25:28.30,0:25:30.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Till then, this money will be rotting away in our account in any case
Dialogue: 3,0:25:31.66,0:25:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们把它投资到市场上，钱就会增长，市场也会增长
Dialogue: 2,0:25:31.66,0:25:34.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If we invest it in the market, the money will grow and so will the market
Dialogue: 3,0:25:34.78,0:25:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事情败露的时候，我们的麻烦也会增加
Dialogue: 2,0:25:34.78,0:25:37.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And when it comes out in the open, our troubles will grow too
Dialogue: 3,0:25:37.66,0:25:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不会有任何麻烦，我们不偷东西
Dialogue: 2,0:25:37.66,0:25:40.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There wont be any trouble We are not stealing
Dialogue: 3,0:25:41.26,0:25:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}钱在我们的账户里，我们怎么处理这笔钱不关别人的事
Dialogue: 2,0:25:41.26,0:25:44.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The money is lying in our account What we do with it is nobodys concern
Dialogue: 3,0:25:44.70,0:25:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想象一下，我们10天能赚多少钱！
Dialogue: 2,0:25:44.70,0:25:47.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Imagine How much profit we can make in 10 days!
Dialogue: 3,0:25:58.86,0:26:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]公牛回到了交易所
Dialogue: 2,0:25:58.86,0:26:02.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] The Bull was back in BSE
Dialogue: 3,0:26:05.50,0:26:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他的第一个赌注就是 ACC
Dialogue: 2,0:26:05.50,0:26:08.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And his first bet, was on ACC
Dialogue: 3,0:26:08.74,0:26:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而熊正在摧毁 ACC
Dialogue: 2,0:26:08.74,0:26:10.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The bears were destroying ACC
Dialogue: 3,0:26:10.90,0:26:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是他们没有任何暗示 
Dialogue: 2,0:26:10.90,0:26:13.34,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But they didnt have even the slightest hint
Dialogue: 3,0:26:13.42,0:26:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这一次，哈沙德不仅仅是有钱  
Dialogue: 2,0:26:13.42,0:26:15.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that this time, Harshad didnt just have money
Dialogue: 3,0:26:15.86,0:26:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}  他拥有整个财富集市
Dialogue: 2,0:26:15.86,0:26:18.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}he had the whole bazaar of wealth
Dialogue: 3,0:26:18.70,0:26:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}通常为了节省安全交易的时间,
Dialogue: 2,0:26:18.70,0:26:20.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Often, to save time in security dealings,
Dialogue: 3,0:26:20.98,0:26:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}银行会将资金直接存入经纪人的账户
Dialogue: 2,0:26:20.98,0:26:23.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}banks would deposit funds directly into brokers accounts
Dialogue: 3,0:26:23.42,0:26:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样经纪人就可以在买入之前敲定最好的交易
Dialogue: 2,0:26:23.42,0:26:26.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}so that the broker could crack the best deals before buying
Dialogue: 3,0:26:26.26,0:26:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈萨德看到了这里的漏洞
Dialogue: 2,0:26:26.26,0:26:28.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad saw the loophole here
Dialogue: 3,0:26:28.18,0:26:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在这笔钱存在他的账户里，他又开始投资股市了
Dialogue: 2,0:26:28.18,0:26:31.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}With this money now lying in his account, he began investing in the share market again
Dialogue: 3,0:26:35.54,0:26:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是一个缓慢的系统 
Dialogue: 2,0:26:35.54,0:26:36.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It was a slow system
Dialogue: 3,0:26:36.94,0:26:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以这笔钱通常会在经纪人的账户里存两个星期
Dialogue: 2,0:26:36.94,0:26:40.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}so the money would often remain in the brokers account for upto a fortnight
Dialogue: 3,0:26:40.98,0:26:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈萨德可以轻易地把它当作自己的 
Dialogue: 2,0:26:40.98,0:26:43.34,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It was readily available for Harshad to use as his own
Dialogue: 3,0:26:43.46,0:26:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}推高任何他喜欢的股票
Dialogue: 2,0:26:43.46,0:26:46.06,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and push up any stock he liked
Dialogue: 3,0:27:01.86,0:27:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}通过在股票市场上轮换银行资金 
Dialogue: 2,0:27:01.86,0:27:04.34,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}By rotating banking funds in the share market
Dialogue: 3,0:27:04.42,0:27:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)} 他赚了很多钱 
Dialogue: 2,0:27:04.42,0:27:06.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}he was making so much profit
Dialogue: 3,0:27:06.42,0:27:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他开始以较低的佣金进行货币市场交易
Dialogue: 2,0:27:06.42,0:27:09.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that he began making money market deals at lower commissions
Dialogue: 3,0:27:12.22,0:27:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}银行得到了最好的交易 
Dialogue: 2,0:27:12.22,0:27:14.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Banks were getting the best deals
Dialogue: 3,0:27:14.26,0:27:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德赚的钱也越来越多
Dialogue: 2,0:27:14.26,0:27:16.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And Harshad was making more and more profit
Dialogue: 3,0:27:17.02,0:27:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对他来说，货币市场已经变成了赚钱的市场
Dialogue: 2,0:27:17.02,0:27:20.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The money market had turned into a money-making market for him
Dialogue: 3,0:27:20.22,0:27:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然，我们可以加入
Dialogue: 2,0:27:20.22,0:27:21.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sure, we can join this
Dialogue: 3,0:27:22.06,0:27:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}夫人，在孟买这样一个黄金地段，有这么大的一套公寓，是很少见的
Dialogue: 2,0:27:22.06,0:27:27.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Madam, a flat this big in Bombay at such a prime location, is rare
Dialogue: 3,0:27:50.58,0:27:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sensex 指数触及1400点
Dialogue: 2,0:27:50.58,0:27:52.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The Sensex is touching 1400
Dialogue: 3,0:27:53.30,0:27:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们应该在1600点时出手
Dialogue: 2,0:27:53.30,0:27:55.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}At 1600 we should start selling
Dialogue: 3,0:27:55.94,0:27:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我希望你不介意
Dialogue: 2,0:27:55.94,0:27:57.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I hope you are okay with that
Dialogue: 3,0:27:57.54,0:27:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}股票市场是你的领域
Dialogue: 2,0:27:57.54,0:27:58.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Share markets are your territory
Dialogue: 3,0:27:59.74,0:28:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}做你认为最好的事情
Dialogue: 2,0:27:59.74,0:28:01.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do what you feel is best
Dialogue: 3,0:28:03.18,0:28:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，如果指数进一步上升呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:03.18,0:28:06.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But, what if the index rises even more?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:06.90,0:28:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德非常乐观
Dialogue: 2,0:28:06.90,0:28:08.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad is being really bullish
Dialogue: 3,0:28:09.06,0:28:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}快点! 快点，他是谁? 他有多少钱？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:09.06,0:28:12.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come on! Come on, who is he? How much money does he have?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:13.10,0:28:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他不能再买下去了
Dialogue: 2,0:28:13.10,0:28:14.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He cant just go on buying more and more
Dialogue: 3,0:28:15.90,0:28:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看吧，你没明白我的意思
Dialogue: 2,0:28:15.90,0:28:17.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}See, you are not getting the point
Dialogue: 3,0:28:19.06,0:28:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他有钱
Dialogue: 2,0:28:19.06,0:28:20.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He has the funds
Dialogue: 3,0:28:21.62,0:28:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他正在利用银行资金推高市场
Dialogue: 2,0:28:21.62,0:28:25.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hes using banking funds to push up the markets
Dialogue: 3,0:28:27.90,0:28:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他反应很快？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:27.90,0:28:29.06,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hes caught on quick?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:30.02,0:28:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他在玩我们的一个小把戏
Dialogue: 2,0:28:30.02,0:28:31.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hes using a trick out of our book
Dialogue: 3,0:28:32.58,0:28:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}唯一的区别是，我们这样做是安全的，而且用一个优雅的方式
Dialogue: 2,0:28:32.58,0:28:37.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The only difference is that we do it safely, and in a classy way
Dialogue: 3,0:28:38.18,0:28:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且他的方式是无阶级的，粗鲁的
Dialogue: 2,0:28:38.18,0:28:41.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And he does it in a classless, crude way
Dialogue: 3,0:28:41.46,0:28:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不
Dialogue: 2,0:28:41.46,0:28:42.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No
Dialogue: 3,0:28:43.42,0:28:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们需要一个策略来阻止他
Dialogue: 2,0:28:43.42,0:28:45.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We need a strategy to stop him
Dialogue: 3,0:28:46.78,0:28:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}用我们的银行资金做空市场
Dialogue: 2,0:28:46.78,0:28:49.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Lets use our banking funds to short the markets
Dialogue: 3,0:28:53.18,0:28:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们必须尽我们所能
Dialogue: 2,0:28:53.18,0:28:54.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have to do whatever we can
Dialogue: 3,0:28:56.54,0:28:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}攻击，分散，交火
Dialogue: 2,0:28:56.54,0:28:58.34,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Attack, divide, engage
Dialogue: 3,0:28:59.62,0:29:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}最终击败
Dialogue: 2,0:28:59.62,0:29:00.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and defeat
Dialogue: 3,0:29:04.94,0:29:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}渣打希望获得价值2亿卢比的证券
Dialogue: 2,0:29:04.94,0:29:07.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Stanchart wants securities worth 200 crores
Dialogue: 3,0:29:07.78,0:29:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 所以呢?-所以是什么意思？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:07.78,0:29:10.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- So? - What do you mean, so?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:11.42,0:29:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们的银行没有一家持有如此巨额的证券
Dialogue: 2,0:29:11.42,0:29:14.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}None of our banks hold such a huge amount of securities
Dialogue: 3,0:29:15.66,0:29:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我
Dialogue: 2,0:29:15.66,0:29:16.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell me something
Dialogue: 3,0:29:16.50,0:29:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们多久向银行提供一次实物证券？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:16.50,0:29:19.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How often have we delivered physical securities to banks?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:21.22,0:29:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们有没有亲自交给他们？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:21.22,0:29:22.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have we ever handed them over in person?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:23.42,0:29:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，兄弟，我们必须给 BRs 作为证据，不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:23.42,0:29:26.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But brother, we have to give BRs as proof, dont we?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:27.02,0:29:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦银行开出收据,
Dialogue: 2,0:29:27.02,0:29:28.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once the bank gives the receipt,
Dialogue: 3,0:29:28.30,0:29:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这意味着他们正在确认收到的证券
Dialogue: 2,0:29:28.30,0:29:30.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It means theyre confirming that the securities received
Dialogue: 3,0:29:30.54,0:29:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}像驴子一样思考，你将永远是一个驴子
Dialogue: 2,0:29:30.54,0:29:32.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Think like a donkey and youll remain one
Dialogue: 3,0:29:32.50,0:29:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:32.50,0:29:33.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:33.50,0:29:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}渣打银行想要价值2亿的 BRs，对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:33.50,0:29:35.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Stanchart wants BRs worth 200 crores, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:36.14,0:29:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 是的-所以我们会给 BRs
Dialogue: 2,0:29:36.14,0:29:37.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Yes - So, well give BRs
Dialogue: 3,0:29:38.46,0:29:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不正是花旗银行的集团所做的吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:38.46,0:29:39.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Isnt that what Citibank cartel does?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:43.66,0:29:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，这种事我做不到?
Dialogue: 2,0:29:43.66,0:29:47.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Bhai, how can I do what you are asking me to?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:47.82,0:29:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 这不合法-这没什么不对的
Dialogue: 2,0:29:47.82,0:29:50.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- This is not legal - Theres nothing wrong in it
Dialogue: 3,0:29:50.74,0:29:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，如果我没有证券，我怎么能够发行 BRs 给他们 ？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:50.74,0:29:55.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But if I dont have the securities, how can I issue BRs to them?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:55.94,0:30:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我怎样才能卖掉我没有的东西还给你一张收据呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:55.94,0:30:00.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How can I sell something I dont have and give you a receipt for it?
Dialogue: 3,0:30:01.38,0:30:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 这是不对的-这不是不对，这是生存
Dialogue: 2,0:30:01.38,0:30:04.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- This is wrong - This is not wrong Its survival
Dialogue: 3,0:30:05.26,0:30:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道你连员工工资都开不出来
Dialogue: 2,0:30:05.26,0:30:08.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Im aware that you dont even have funds to pay salaries
Dialogue: 3,0:30:09.30,0:30:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此，这是挽救你的一个可行的方法
Dialogue: 2,0:30:09.30,0:30:11.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, this is a sure-shot way to rescue your bank from its losses
Dialogue: 3,0:30:11.78,0:30:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这很简单
Dialogue: 2,0:30:11.78,0:30:12.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Its very simple
Dialogue: 3,0:30:13.34,0:30:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}渣打银行想要价值2亿的证券？
Dialogue: 2,0:30:13.34,0:30:15.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Stanchart wants securities worth 200 crores?
Dialogue: 3,0:30:15.74,0:30:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你只需要开出收据
Dialogue: 2,0:30:15.74,0:30:16.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You just issue the BRs
Dialogue: 3,0:30:17.74,0:30:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}把收据给他们
Dialogue: 2,0:30:17.74,0:30:18.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Give them the receipt
Dialogue: 3,0:30:19.58,0:30:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦他们拿到收据，20亿卢比就会打到你的账户上
Dialogue: 2,0:30:19.58,0:30:21.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}As soon as they get the receipt, 200 crores will be in your account
Dialogue: 3,0:30:22.58,0:30:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}其中有四千万是你的
Dialogue: 2,0:30:22.58,0:30:25.06,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Of which, 4 crores will be yours Bankerage
Dialogue: 3,0:30:26.46,0:30:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}15天内，我会还给他们20亿卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:30:26.46,0:30:28.34,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Within 15 days, Ill return 200 crores to them
Dialogue: 3,0:30:28.42,0:30:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们会把 BRs 还给你，然后把它们撕掉，如果你愿意的话
Dialogue: 2,0:30:28.42,0:30:30.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Theyll return the BRs to you Then tear them off, if you like
Dialogue: 3,0:30:31.86,0:30:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们将得到证券
Dialogue: 2,0:30:31.86,0:30:34.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They will get the securities
Dialogue: 3,0:30:34.34,0:30:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你会得到佣金
Dialogue: 2,0:30:34.34,0:30:35.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You will get a commission
Dialogue: 3,0:30:36.22,0:30:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}花旗银行的所有业务都是通过 BRs 进行的
Dialogue: 2,0:30:36.22,0:30:38.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Citibank does all its business through BRs
Dialogue: 3,0:30:39.46,0:30:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，先生，即使你知道,
Dialogue: 2,0:30:39.46,0:30:40.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And look sir, even you know,
Dialogue: 3,0:30:40.78,0:30:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在任何交易中，实物证券都不会被交换
Dialogue: 2,0:30:40.78,0:30:43.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that physical securities are never exchanged in any deal
