Dialogue: 3,0:30:51.38,0:30:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度央行行长知道 
Dialogue: 2,0:30:51.38,0:30:52.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The RBI Governor knew
