Dialogue: 2,0:30:52.98,0:30:56.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}banks will play a pivotal role in Indias economic revival
Dialogue: 3,0:30:56.22,0:30:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是印度储备银行也开始注意到
