Dialogue: 2,0:30:59.34,0:31:01.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}in the security dealings of banks
Dialogue: 3,0:31:01.46,0:31:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但这是一个前数字时代
Dialogue: 2,0:31:01.46,0:31:03.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But this was a pre-digital era
Dialogue: 3,0:31:03.54,0:31:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}  通常需要好几天才能追踪到一笔交易
Dialogue: 2,0:31:03.54,0:31:06.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}when it often took days to trace a transaction
Dialogue: 3,0:31:06.34,0:31:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}找到一份文件需要几个月的时间
Dialogue: 2,0:31:06.34,0:31:08.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and months to locate a file
Dialogue: 3,0:31:08.38,0:31:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对印度储备银行来说，这将是一场乏味且持久的战斗
Dialogue: 2,0:31:08.38,0:31:10.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}For RBI, this was going to be a tedious battle
