Dialogue: 2,0:31:13.38,0:31:16.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}United Bank of India, Bank of Baroda
Dialogue: 3,0:31:16.94,0:31:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度银行、卡纳拉银行和印度银行
Dialogue: 2,0:31:16.94,0:31:19.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bank of India, Canara Bank and Indian Bank
Dialogue: 3,0:31:20.30,0:31:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}与银行业务运营和发展部联系
Dialogue: 2,0:31:20.30,0:31:23.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Talk to the Department of Banking Operations and Development
Dialogue: 3,0:31:24.34,0:31:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要所有这些银行的安全部门
Dialogue: 2,0:31:24.34,0:31:26.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I want the security departments of all these banks
