Dialogue: 2,0:31:26.54,0:31:27.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}thoroughly checked and inspected
Dialogue: 3,0:31:29.30,0:31:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生 呃
Dialogue: 2,0:31:29.30,0:31:30.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir Uh
Dialogue: 3,0:31:33.10,0:31:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 什么事，高希?-先生，花旗银行？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:33.10,0:31:35.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Yes, Ghosh? - Sir, Citibank?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:39.78,0:31:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯，这是一家外国银行，我们必须小心
Dialogue: 2,0:31:39.78,0:31:41.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hmmm Its a foreign bank We have to be careful
Dialogue: 3,0:31:43.22,0:31:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们的经济仍在复苏，尚未企稳
Dialogue: 2,0:31:43.22,0:31:45.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Our economy is still recovering It hasnt stabilised yet
