Dialogue: 2,0:31:47.94,0:31:50.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are still dependent on the loans arranged by them
Dialogue: 3,0:31:52.06,0:31:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样
Dialogue: 2,0:31:52.06,0:31:53.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do one thing
