Dialogue: 2,0:32:03.06,0:32:04.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not an investigation
Dialogue: 3,0:32:05.70,0:32:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这件事不应该传出去
Dialogue: 2,0:32:05.70,0:32:07.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The matter shouldnt leave this room
Dialogue: 3,0:32:08.42,0:32:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不能让媒体知道，谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:32:08.42,0:32:10.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The Press mustnt get to know of it Thank you
Dialogue: 3,0:32:10.82,0:32:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}第五家银行是哪家? 印度银行？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:10.82,0:32:13.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And which is the fifth bank? Indian Bank?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:13.82,0:32:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太好了，你确定吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:13.82,0:32:14.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Great Are you sure?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:15.58,0:32:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你确定今天所有这些银行都会接受检查吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:15.58,0:32:17.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And youre sure there will be inspections in all these banks today?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:18.14,0:32:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}女士，这只是前五家银行
Dialogue: 2,0:32:18.14,0:32:20.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Man] Madam, these are only the first five banks
Dialogue: 3,0:32:20.90,0:32:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度储备银行将会盯上其他银行
Dialogue: 2,0:32:20.90,0:32:22.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The RBI will go after other banks too
Dialogue: 3,0:32:23.70,0:32:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有这些混蛋现在都暴露了
Dialogue: 2,0:32:23.70,0:32:25.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All these b******s stand exposed now
Dialogue: 3,0:32:25.66,0:32:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使是像卡拉季银行这样的小银行
Dialogue: 2,0:32:25.66,0:32:27.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Even small banks like Bank of Karaj
Dialogue: 3,0:32:28.02,0:32:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那里根本没有证券账户
Dialogue: 2,0:32:28.02,0:32:29.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No account of securities there either
Dialogue: 3,0:32:29.98,0:32:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}RBI（印度储备银行）的计划是什么? 我是说，他们的下一步计划是什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:29.98,0:32:32.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, whats RBI planning? I mean, whats their next step going to be?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:33.50,0:32:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}像往常一样，他们会发布有关证券买卖的通知
Dialogue: 2,0:32:33.50,0:32:36.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Man] As usual, theyll issue a circular on the buying and selling of securities
Dialogue: 3,0:32:36.54,0:32:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度储备银行将发布新规则
Dialogue: 2,0:32:36.54,0:32:37.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}RBI will issue new rules
Dialogue: 3,0:32:37.94,0:32:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还会增加一些分数，还有什么
Dialogue: 2,0:32:37.94,0:32:39.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And theyll add some more points, what else?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:40.02,0:32:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你能把我和任何经纪人联系起来吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:40.02,0:32:41.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can you link me to any broker?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:41.58,0:32:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哦，不行，除非这次检查的消息公之于众  
Dialogue: 2,0:32:41.58,0:32:44.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Man] Oh no Unless the news of this inspection goes public
Dialogue: 3,0:32:44.54,0:32:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有的经纪人都会守口如瓶
Dialogue: 2,0:32:44.54,0:32:46.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}all the brokers will keep their mouth shut
Dialogue: 3,0:32:47.10,0:32:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有没有人有理由会开口？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:47.10,0:32:48.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Does anybody ever speak without a reason?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:49.02,0:32:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是理由是可以创造的，不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:49.02,0:32:50.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But reasons can be created, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:52.10,0:32:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]尽管哈尔沙德和印度储备银行都把目光放在了银行身上
Dialogue: 2,0:32:52.10,0:32:55.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] While both Harshad and the RBI kept their sights focused on the banks
Dialogue: 3,0:32:55.78,0:32:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我仍在专注于我在《印度时报》的新工作
Dialogue: 2,0:32:55.78,0:32:58.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I was focused on my new job with The Times of India
Dialogue: 3,0:32:59.18,0:33:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们谁也不知道我们的道路很快就会相交
Dialogue: 2,0:32:59.18,0:33:02.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}None of us knew that our paths were going to cross very soon
Dialogue: 3,0:33:03.18,0:33:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也没有一家银行的名称或来源
Dialogue: 2,0:33:03.18,0:33:05.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Nor is there the name of a bank nor a source
Dialogue: 3,0:33:07.14,0:33:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔，没有任何名字，我不能发表这个
Dialogue: 2,0:33:07.14,0:33:09.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta, without any names, I cant print this
Dialogue: 3,0:33:09.34,0:33:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的线人在其中一家银行工作
Dialogue: 2,0:33:09.34,0:33:11.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My source works in one of these banks
Dialogue: 3,0:33:11.06,0:33:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个故事百分之百是真的
Dialogue: 2,0:33:11.06,0:33:12.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The story is 100 percent legit
Dialogue: 3,0:33:12.34,0:33:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也许吧，但是有人能证明吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:12.34,0:33:14.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Maybe But can anyone confirm it?
Dialogue: 3,0:33:14.98,0:33:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我不能-拉杰迪普，这个故事很重要
Dialogue: 2,0:33:14.98,0:33:16.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- I cant - Rajdeep, this story is huge
Dialogue: 3,0:33:16.94,0:33:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且会越来越重要，但只有当你发表这个
Dialogue: 2,0:33:16.94,0:33:18.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And it will only get bigger, but only if you print this
Dialogue: 3,0:33:19.34,0:33:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 苏切塔，你知道我的答案-你要相信我
Dialogue: 2,0:33:19.34,0:33:22.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Rajdeep] Sucheta, you know my answer - You need to trust me
Dialogue: 3,0:33:22.38,0:33:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当其他媒体都在赞扬拉詹 · 皮莱的时候
Dialogue: 2,0:33:22.38,0:33:24.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When the rest of the media was singing Rajan Pillais praises
Dialogue: 3,0:33:24.62,0:33:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是我举报他在新加坡触犯了法律，结果越来越严重
Dialogue: 2,0:33:24.62,0:33:27.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I was the one who reported his brush with the law in Singapore and it snowballed
Dialogue: 3,0:33:27.74,0:33:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我有同样的预感，把它发表出来
Dialogue: 2,0:33:27.74,0:33:30.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have the same hunch with this Print it
Dialogue: 3,0:33:30.38,0:33:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只有这样，银行体系中的每个人才会知道 
Dialogue: 2,0:33:30.38,0:33:32.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Only then will everyone in the banking system know
Dialogue: 3,0:33:32.26,0:33:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}内部消息不可能永远隐藏
Dialogue: 2,0:33:32.26,0:33:34.34,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that inside information cant stay hidden forever
Dialogue: 3,0:33:34.78,0:33:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们发表了这个之后就没人开口了
Dialogue: 2,0:33:34.78,0:33:37.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And if we print this, and no one opens their mouth after that
Dialogue: 3,0:33:38.34,0:33:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后呢? 我不能冒险把这个放在头版
Dialogue: 2,0:33:38.34,0:33:40.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then? I cant risk putting this on the front page
Dialogue: 3,0:33:45.26,0:33:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你会把它放在哪里?-财经板块
Dialogue: 2,0:33:45.26,0:33:47.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Where will you put it? - The financial section
Dialogue: 3,0:33:51.82,0:33:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}绝对不是，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:33:51.82,0:33:53.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No chance, sir No chance
Dialogue: 3,0:33:53.94,0:33:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可以肯定，这个消息绝对不是从我们这边泄露出去的
Dialogue: 2,0:33:53.94,0:33:56.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Im absolutely sure, this information hasnt leaked from our end
Dialogue: 3,0:33:56.78,0:33:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是某家银行寄来的
Dialogue: 2,0:33:56.78,0:33:57.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Its from some bank
Dialogue: 3,0:33:58.26,0:34:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是既然这个消息已经公开了
Dialogue: 2,0:33:58.26,0:34:00.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But since this news is already out in the open
Dialogue: 3,0:34:00.74,0:34:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们可以宣布一次常规审计来确认违规行为吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:00.74,0:34:04.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}can we announce a proper audit to confirm the irregularities?
Dialogue: 3,0:34:07.26,0:34:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}公众不想接受审计
Dialogue: 2,0:34:07.26,0:34:08.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The public doesnt want an audit
Dialogue: 3,0:34:10.10,0:34:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，高希，那没用的
Dialogue: 2,0:34:10.10,0:34:11.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, Ghosh, that wont work
Dialogue: 3,0:34:13.50,0:34:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}发布一个指示并与媒体分享
Dialogue: 2,0:34:13.50,0:34:16.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Issue a directive and share it with the press
Dialogue: 3,0:34:17.38,0:34:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都必须清楚地知道
Dialogue: 2,0:34:17.38,0:34:19.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone must know clearly
Dialogue: 3,0:34:19.26,0:34:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度储备银行已经发布了关于 BRs 使用的严格指导方针
Dialogue: 2,0:34:19.26,0:34:22.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that the RBI has issued strict guidelines on the use of BRs
Dialogue: 3,0:34:27.62,0:34:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}凯迪亚告诉我，你拒绝了所有的远期交易
Dialogue: 2,0:34:27.62,0:34:30.06,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Tyagi] Kedia told me that youve refused all ready forward deals?
Dialogue: 3,0:34:31.42,0:34:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，印度储备银行就在我们后面
Dialogue: 2,0:34:31.42,0:34:33.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, The RBI is on our tail, sir
Dialogue: 3,0:34:33.14,0:34:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是如果你都掩盖好了，又怎么会有问题呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:33.14,0:34:34.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But where is the problem if youre all covered up?
Dialogue: 3,0:34:35.98,0:34:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，印度储备银行已经发布了一份新的通知
Dialogue: 2,0:34:35.98,0:34:38.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, RBI has issued a new circular
Dialogue: 3,0:34:39.02,0:34:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，你没有看过指导方针吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:39.02,0:34:40.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Havent you read the guidelines, Sir?
Dialogue: 3,0:34:42.74,0:34:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看看这个，先生，这是严格的命令
Dialogue: 2,0:34:42.74,0:34:45.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look at this, sir These are strict orders
Dialogue: 3,0:34:45.54,0:34:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有准备就绪的远期交易  
Dialogue: 2,0:34:45.54,0:34:47.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All ready forward transactions
Dialogue: 3,0:34:47.54,0:34:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}  不管是通过 SGL 还是 BR
Dialogue: 2,0:34:47.54,0:34:50.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}whether through the mechanism of SGL or BR
Dialogue: 3,0:34:50.62,0:34:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}  应该在同一天反映在其投资帐户
Dialogue: 2,0:34:50.62,0:34:53.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}should be reflected on the same day in its investment account
Dialogue: 3,0:34:54.06,0:34:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一家银行与另一家银行之间的交易  
Dialogue: 2,0:34:54.06,0:34:56.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Transactions between one bank and another bank
Dialogue: 3,0:34:56.62,0:34:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}  不应该通过经纪人的账户
Dialogue: 2,0:34:56.62,0:34:58.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}should not be put through the brokers accounts
Dialogue: 3,0:34:59.38,0:35:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}银行不应充当任何经纪客户的代理人
Dialogue: 2,0:34:59.38,0:35:02.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Banks should not act as agents for any broker clients
Dialogue: 3,0:35:04.14,0:35:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}最重要的是
Dialogue: 2,0:35:04.14,0:35:05.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And the most important part
Dialogue: 3,0:35:06.42,0:35:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有交易都应严格按照市场利率进行
Dialogue: 2,0:35:06.42,0:35:09.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All transactions should be at market rates, strictly
Dialogue: 3,0:35:10.30,0:35:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有
Dialogue: 2,0:35:10.30,0:35:11.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And
Dialogue: 3,0:35:11.50,0:35:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你从来不按市价交易-别说了
Dialogue: 2,0:35:11.50,0:35:14.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- You never deal at market rates - Stop it
Dialogue: 3,0:35:15.02,0:35:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是RBI，又不是 CBI（印度中央调查局）
Dialogue: 2,0:35:15.02,0:35:16.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Its RBI, not the CBI
Dialogue: 3,0:35:17.46,0:35:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些只是指导方针，不是法律
Dialogue: 2,0:35:17.46,0:35:19.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And these are guidelines, not the law
Dialogue: 3,0:35:19.74,0:35:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是印度
Dialogue: 2,0:35:19.74,0:35:20.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And this is India
Dialogue: 3,0:35:21.46,0:35:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Tyagi ]你知道这里什么都没发生过
Dialogue: 2,0:35:21.46,0:35:23.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Tyagi] You know nothing ever happens here
Dialogue: 3,0:35:24.18,0:35:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你还想继续做生意
Dialogue: 2,0:35:24.18,0:35:26.34,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And look, if you want to stay in business
Dialogue: 3,0:35:27.26,0:35:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那你就得做生意了，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:35:27.26,0:35:28.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}then youll have to do business, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:35:29.34,0:35:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起，特亚吉先生
Dialogue: 2,0:35:29.34,0:35:30.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Im sorry, Mr Tyagi
Dialogue: 3,0:35:31.90,0:35:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我们会坚持指导方针
Dialogue: 2,0:35:31.90,0:35:33.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But well stick to the guidelines for any business
Dialogue: 3,0:35:38.22,0:35:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是说我老了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:35:38.22,0:35:40.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You tell me Am I old?
Dialogue: 3,0:35:41.30,0:35:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}新一代人就是不听
Dialogue: 2,0:35:41.30,0:35:43.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This new generation just wont listen
