Dialogue: 3,0:35:53.58,0:35:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是他没有听进去，你看看，现在每一笔交易都是一场斗争
Dialogue: 2,0:35:53.58,0:35:57.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But he didnt listen And look Today, every deal is a struggle
