Dialogue: 2,0:36:02.10,0:36:04.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Suresh] Why dont you explain this to my son? - But you never introduced us!
Dialogue: 3,0:36:05.30,0:36:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会解释所有关于年龄的问题，也要跟进那个虚假BR的报道
Dialogue: 2,0:36:05.30,0:36:08.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I wouldve explained all about age and also taken a follow-up on that fake BR story
Dialogue: 3,0:36:08.86,0:36:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哦，那么，我现在没用了？
Dialogue: 2,0:36:08.86,0:36:11.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh So, Im useless now?
Dialogue: 3,0:36:11.34,0:36:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}新的消息来源，新的故事？
Dialogue: 2,0:36:11.34,0:36:12.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}New source New story?
Dialogue: 3,0:36:12.66,0:36:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏雷什 好吧，为什么我叫你苏雷什？
Dialogue: 2,0:36:12.66,0:36:14.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Suresh Okay, why do I call you Suresh?
Dialogue: 3,0:36:15.22,0:36:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为你是我的朋友，而不仅仅是我的消息来源
Dialogue: 2,0:36:15.22,0:36:16.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because youre a friend and not just a source
Dialogue: 3,0:36:17.14,0:36:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都压制了 BR 的报道
Dialogue: 2,0:36:17.14,0:36:19.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone has suppressed the BR story
Dialogue: 3,0:36:19.42,0:36:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我没有后续报道，这件事就不了了之了
Dialogue: 2,0:36:19.42,0:36:21.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And if I dont get a follow-up, it will die
Dialogue: 3,0:36:21.98,0:36:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，我见到他的时候会和他谈谈的
Dialogue: 2,0:36:21.98,0:36:23.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay, Ill talk to him when I see him
Dialogue: 3,0:36:23.94,0:36:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 他可能会同意-他不是在办公室吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:36:23.94,0:36:25.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- He might agree - Isnt he in the office?
Dialogue: 3,0:36:26.10,0:36:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他每时每刻都在办公室里
Dialogue: 2,0:36:26.10,0:36:28.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hes in office 24/7
