Dialogue: 2,0:36:28.62,0:36:32.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But despite being next-door he doesnt even talk to me, let alone meeting
Dialogue: 3,0:36:34.26,0:36:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，我先走了
