Dialogue: 2,0:36:51.70,0:36:52.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[DT] I know who you are
Dialogue: 3,0:36:52.98,0:36:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不想和你说话
Dialogue: 2,0:36:52.98,0:36:54.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I dont want to speak to you
Dialogue: 3,0:36:54.30,0:36:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，没关系，你父亲已经认识我了
Dialogue: 2,0:36:54.30,0:36:56.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Listen, its okay Your father already knows me
Dialogue: 3,0:36:56.18,0:36:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我只需要一点点信息-要我叫保安吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:36:56.18,0:36:58.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- I just need a little bit of info - Do you want me to call the security?
Dialogue: 3,0:36:58.90,0:37:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不不 请不要误会我
Dialogue: 2,0:36:58.90,0:37:00.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No no Please, dont misunderstand me
