Dialogue: 2,0:37:04.42,0:37:07.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay, your father has my number if you ever want to talk
Dialogue: 3,0:37:09.90,0:37:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，抱歉，谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:37:09.90,0:37:11.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay Sorry Thank you
