Dialogue: 2,0:37:15.94,0:37:20.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The RBI is checking every line from every page of every book
Dialogue: 3,0:37:21.58,0:37:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，让我们像银行家一样谈谈
Dialogue: 2,0:37:21.58,0:37:22.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay Lets talk like bankers
Dialogue: 3,0:37:23.74,0:37:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}忘了证券吧
Dialogue: 2,0:37:23.74,0:37:24.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Forget the securities
Dialogue: 3,0:37:25.34,0:37:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我肯定你能借给我一笔钱？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:25.34,0:37:27.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Im sure you can give me a loan?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:27.90,0:37:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我，你们能提供多少信用额度？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:27.90,0:37:29.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell me What line of credit can you offer?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:30.10,0:37:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}贷款需要资金，不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:30.10,0:37:32.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}To give a loan, I need funds, dont I?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:32.74,0:37:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我没有拒绝，但是我们面临资金短缺
Dialogue: 2,0:37:32.74,0:37:36.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Im not refusing But were facing a major crunch for funds
Dialogue: 3,0:37:37.30,0:37:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你也是因为资金问题被困在这里的，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:37.30,0:37:38.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You too are stranded because of funds, huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:41.58,0:37:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，那如果
Dialogue: 2,0:37:41.58,0:37:42.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay What if I bring customers
Dialogue: 3,0:37:44.10,0:37:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我带来一个能在这家银行存一大笔钱的客户？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:44.10,0:37:46.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}who will deposit large amounts in this bank?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:46.82,0:37:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么你会给我贷款，对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:46.82,0:37:47.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then you will give me a loan, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:49.94,0:37:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度储备银行已经用它的指导方针束缚了整个系统
Dialogue: 2,0:37:49.94,0:37:53.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] RBI had chained the whole system with its guidelines
Dialogue: 3,0:37:53.82,0:37:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德知道，即使是熊市集团也是在没有现金的情况下进行演习
Dialogue: 2,0:37:53.82,0:37:57.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad knew that even the bear cartel was on a dry-run with no cash
Dialogue: 3,0:37:57.90,0:38:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在是时候走在他们前面了
Dialogue: 2,0:37:57.90,0:38:00.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This was the time to get ahead of them
Dialogue: 3,0:38:00.98,0:38:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}停泊费，燃料费 一共
Dialogue: 2,0:38:00.98,0:38:04.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Docking charges, fuel charges altogether
Dialogue: 3,0:38:04.14,0:38:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们每周收集20到25亿卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:38:04.14,0:38:07.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}they make a weekly collection of 20 to 25 crores
Dialogue: 3,0:38:08.50,0:38:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有那个，液体
Dialogue: 2,0:38:08.50,0:38:09.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And that too, liquid
Dialogue: 3,0:38:10.54,0:38:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在码头和海里，一切都是液态的
Dialogue: 2,0:38:10.54,0:38:12.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everything is liquid at the docks and in the sea
Dialogue: 3,0:38:14.50,0:38:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想象一下
Dialogue: 2,0:38:14.50,0:38:15.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just imagine
Dialogue: 3,0:38:16.26,0:38:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们把他们所有的资金都转移到RICO银行呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:38:16.26,0:38:19.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What if we channelize all their funds to RICO?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:20.10,0:38:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后资金最终会回到我们手中
Dialogue: 2,0:38:20.10,0:38:22.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then the funds will eventually come back to us
Dialogue: 3,0:38:23.22,0:38:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}等等，兄弟，告诉我，你是国王吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:38:23.22,0:38:26.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Wait a minute, brother Tell me something Are you a king?
