Dialogue: 2,0:38:27.30,0:38:28.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Or a LOOTSESEA?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:28.42,0:38:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- lootsesea?-七海之王？
Dialogue: 2,0:38:28.42,0:38:30.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- LOOTSESEA? - Lord Of The Seven Seas?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:31.22,0:38:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你一招手，码头会把他们所有的资金都投入 RICO？
Dialogue: 2,0:38:31.22,0:38:35.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That you will beckon, and the docks will pour their entire fund into RICO?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:35.54,0:38:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}胡说！
Dialogue: 2,0:38:35.54,0:38:36.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Rubbish!
Dialogue: 3,0:38:39.06,0:38:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都会向利益低头
Dialogue: 2,0:38:39.06,0:38:40.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone bows down to profit
