Dialogue: 2,0:38:43.58,0:38:46.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And Bhushan, where these funds should be invested
Dialogue: 3,0:38:46.58,0:38:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是主席的特权
Dialogue: 2,0:38:46.58,0:38:47.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}is the prerogative of the chairman
