Dialogue: 2,0:38:47.78,0:38:49.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All we have to do, is convince the chairman
Dialogue: 3,0:38:49.90,0:38:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你打算编什么故事? 请解释一下
Dialogue: 2,0:38:49.90,0:38:53.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And what is this story you plan to weave? Please explain
Dialogue: 3,0:38:54.22,0:38:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}瞧，RICO 没有资金贷款
Dialogue: 2,0:38:54.22,0:38:56.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, RICO has no funds to give a loan
Dialogue: 3,0:38:56.50,0:38:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果这些钱到了那里，他们就会得到资金
Dialogue: 2,0:38:56.50,0:38:58.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If this money goes there, theyll get funds
Dialogue: 3,0:38:58.38,0:38:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们可以贷款
