Dialogue: 3,0:39:04.50,0:39:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Bhushan ]也就是说，1% 给主席
Dialogue: 2,0:39:04.50,0:39:07.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Bhushan] That means, one percent for the chairman
Dialogue: 3,0:39:08.30,0:39:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是兄弟，钱还是会从我们的口袋里拿出来的，对吧
Dialogue: 2,0:39:08.30,0:39:10.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But brother, the money will still go from our pocket, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:39:10.94,0:39:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，就这样吧
Dialogue: 2,0:39:10.94,0:39:12.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] So, let it
