Dialogue: 3,0:43:15.14,0:43:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但对印度经济而言，1991年是一个奇怪的时期
Dialogue: 2,0:43:15.14,0:43:19.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] But 1991 was a strange time for the Indian economy
Dialogue: 3,0:43:19.94,0:43:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在经济危机中  
Dialogue: 2,0:43:19.94,0:43:21.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In the middle of an economic crisis
Dialogue: 3,0:43:21.66,0:43:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}钱德拉谢卡尔政府解散了
Dialogue: 2,0:43:21.66,0:43:23.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The Chandrashekhar government was dissolved
Dialogue: 3,0:43:24.06,0:43:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}下一次选举是在曼达尔委员会抗议期间举行的
Dialogue: 2,0:43:24.06,0:43:28.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The next election took place in the midst of Mandal Commission protests
Dialogue: 3,0:43:28.78,0:43:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很难猜测选举结果  
Dialogue: 2,0:43:28.78,0:43:31.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It was tough to guess the election result
Dialogue: 3,0:43:31.78,0:43:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但在第一轮投票之后
Dialogue: 2,0:43:31.78,0:43:33.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But after the first round of voting
Dialogue: 3,0:43:33.94,0:43:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}前总理拉吉夫 · 甘地被暗杀
Dialogue: 2,0:43:33.94,0:43:37.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}ex-Prime Minister Rajiv Gandhi was assassinated
Dialogue: 3,0:43:37.10,0:43:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当选举结果公布的时候
Dialogue: 2,0:43:37.10,0:43:39.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And when the election results were announced
Dialogue: 3,0:43:39.10,0:43:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}少数派政府在纳拉辛哈·拉奥的领导下成立
Dialogue: 2,0:43:39.10,0:43:42.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}a minority government was formed under P V Narasimha Rao
Dialogue: 3,0:43:43.02,0:43:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但这些都没有影响到股市
Dialogue: 2,0:43:43.02,0:43:45.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But none of this impacted the share market
Dialogue: 3,0:43:46.62,0:43:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德把指数拉到了极高的水平
Dialogue: 2,0:43:46.62,0:43:50.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad took the BSE index to astronomical heights
Dialogue: 3,0:43:50.58,0:43:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在，没有人能阻止他的奔牛节了
Dialogue: 2,0:43:50.58,0:43:53.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, there was no one to stop his Bull Run
Dialogue: 3,0:43:53.58,0:44:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的朋友，你什么也带不走
Dialogue: 2,0:43:53.58,0:44:05.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You will take nothing with you, my friend
Dialogue: 3,0:44:09.34,0:44:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你空手而来，走的时候也是空手，我的朋友
Dialogue: 2,0:44:09.34,0:44:17.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You came empty-handed And thats how you will go, my friend
Dialogue: 3,0:44:17.98,0:44:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在哈尔沙德之前，没有人能在市场上赚到这么多钱
Dialogue: 2,0:44:17.98,0:44:21.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Before Harshad, no one had made such wealth in the market
Dialogue: 3,0:44:21.74,0:44:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他的生活方式不亚于名人或电影明星
Dialogue: 2,0:44:21.74,0:44:25.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}His lifestyle was no less than a celebrity or a film star
Dialogue: 3,0:44:25.90,0:44:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他白手起家的故事
Dialogue: 2,0:44:25.90,0:44:27.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}With his rags to riches story
Dialogue: 3,0:44:27.50,0:44:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}   他已经成为每个普通印度人的英雄
Dialogue: 2,0:44:27.50,0:44:29.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}he had become a hero for every common Indian
Dialogue: 3,0:44:30.74,0:44:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都想成为哈尔沙德 · 梅塔
Dialogue: 2,0:44:30.74,0:44:33.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And everybody wanted to be Harshad Mehta
Dialogue: 3,0:44:35.58,0:44:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是不是有点过了？
Dialogue: 2,0:44:35.58,0:44:37.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Isnt this a bit much?
Dialogue: 3,0:44:42.34,0:44:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个哈尔沙德 · 梅塔现在越界了
Dialogue: 2,0:44:42.34,0:44:44.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This Harshad Mehta is crossing the line now
Dialogue: 3,0:44:46.54,0:44:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他已经超越了自己的极限
Dialogue: 2,0:44:46.54,0:44:49.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The m**********r is crossing his limits
Dialogue: 3,0:44:49.82,0:44:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}肉体和灵魂只有一个真理
Dialogue: 2,0:44:49.82,0:44:53.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Of this body and this soul theres only one truth
Dialogue: 3,0:44:54.10,0:44:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你必须注意你的行动，收获命运的甜蜜果实
Dialogue: 2,0:44:54.10,0:44:59.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You must watch your actions to reap destinys sweet fruit
Dialogue: 3,0:45:00.02,0:45:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以说伟大的圣人这个世界是虚假的事情
Dialogue: 2,0:45:00.02,0:45:05.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So say the great saints this world is a false affair
Dialogue: 3,0:45:05.34,0:45:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}  毕竟，生活不过是两天的集市 
Dialogue: 2,0:45:05.34,0:45:10.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}After all, life is but a two-day fair
Dialogue: 3,0:45:10.70,0:45:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你给这个世界带来了什么? 你又能从这个世界上带走什么? 
Dialogue: 2,0:45:10.70,0:45:15.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What did you bring into this world And what can you take away from this world
Dialogue: 3,0:45:16.06,0:45:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}  毕竟，生活不过是两天的集市 
Dialogue: 2,0:45:16.06,0:45:31.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}After all, life is but a two-day fair
Dialogue: 3,0:45:32.62,0:45:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}股票市场的逻辑很简单
Dialogue: 2,0:45:32.62,0:45:34.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The logic of the stock market is very easy
Dialogue: 3,0:45:34.58,0:45:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}闭上你的眼睛，随便选一支股票，然后投资它
Dialogue: 2,0:45:34.58,0:45:37.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Close your eyes, pick any stock and invest in it
Dialogue: 3,0:45:37.54,0:45:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}获胜或失败的机会总是一半一半
Dialogue: 2,0:45:37.54,0:45:40.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The chances of winning or losing are always 50-50
Dialogue: 3,0:45:41.74,0:45:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别笑，这是事实
Dialogue: 2,0:45:41.74,0:45:43.34,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Dont laugh, its a fact
Dialogue: 3,0:45:44.22,0:45:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道吗，1964年在美国，人们让一只猴子选择15支股票
Dialogue: 2,0:45:44.22,0:45:47.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Did you know, in 1964 in the US, a monkey was made to select 15 scrips
Dialogue: 3,0:45:48.90,0:45:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也是这样，蒙着眼睛扔飞镖
Dialogue: 2,0:45:48.90,0:45:51.14,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That too, by throwing darts with a blindfold
Dialogue: 3,0:45:53.66,0:45:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}与此同时，一位金融专家又选择了另外15支股
Dialogue: 2,0:45:53.66,0:45:56.46,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And at the same time, a financial expert selected another 15 scrips
Dialogue: 3,0:45:57.06,0:45:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}结果是什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:45:57.06,0:45:58.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What was the result?
Dialogue: 3,0:45:58.70,0:46:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}猴子赢了
Dialogue: 2,0:45:58.70,0:46:00.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The 15 scrips selected by the monkey, won
Dialogue: 3,0:46:02.50,0:46:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们赚了一大笔钱
Dialogue: 2,0:46:02.50,0:46:03.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They made a huge profit
Dialogue: 3,0:46:04.70,0:46:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场有一个简单的哲学: 投资，放松
Dialogue: 2,0:46:04.70,0:46:07.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The market has a simple philosophy Invest, and relax
Dialogue: 3,0:46:08.10,0:46:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 他也是这么做的-不
Dialogue: 2,0:46:08.10,0:46:09.98,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Even he did the same - No
Dialogue: 3,0:46:10.46,0:46:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的意思是，是的，有一点
Dialogue: 2,0:46:10.46,0:46:11.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean yes, a little bit
Dialogue: 3,0:46:12.94,0:46:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}叔叔，能给我签个名吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:46:12.94,0:46:15.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Uncle, can I get your autograph, please?
Dialogue: 3,0:46:21.34,0:46:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}亲爱的，他们叫我阿米塔布·巴沙坎，但实际上我不是他
Dialogue: 2,0:46:21.34,0:46:23.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Dear, they call me Amitabh Bachchan, but Im actually not him
Dialogue: 3,0:46:29.18,0:46:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我告诉过你，我不想要这些旧的
Dialogue: 2,0:46:29.18,0:46:31.18,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I had told you, I dont want these old ones
Dialogue: 3,0:46:31.30,0:46:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我看看新的东西
Dialogue: 2,0:46:31.30,0:46:32.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Show me something new
Dialogue: 3,0:46:32.70,0:46:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是国王的座驾
Dialogue: 2,0:46:32.70,0:46:34.70,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the car of the King of Partan, Harshad Bhai
Dialogue: 3,0:46:35.54,0:46:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}整个印度只有一辆
Dialogue: 2,0:46:35.54,0:46:36.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A single piece in all of India
Dialogue: 3,0:46:37.50,0:46:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}1200 CC的发动机
Dialogue: 2,0:46:37.50,0:46:39.34,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And it has a 1200 CC engine
Dialogue: 3,0:46:40.58,0:46:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}亲爱的，现在是我的时代
Dialogue: 2,0:46:40.58,0:46:42.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Darling, this is my time
Dialogue: 3,0:46:42.42,0:46:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以不只是你们国王的车，我还可以买下他的宫殿
Dialogue: 2,0:46:42.42,0:46:44.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So not just your Kings car, I can buy his palace
Dialogue: 3,0:46:45.98,0:46:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 给我看点新的，进口的-你知道进口车是怎么回事
Dialogue: 2,0:46:45.98,0:46:48.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Show me something new Imported -[Dealer] You know how it is with imported cars
Dialogue: 3,0:46:49.06,0:46:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们一个月几乎都没有一辆
Dialogue: 2,0:46:49.06,0:46:50.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We hardly get one in a month
Dialogue: 3,0:46:51.62,0:46:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}下个月有一辆雷克萨斯从迪拜开过来
Dialogue: 2,0:46:51.62,0:46:53.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Theres a Lexus coming from Dubai next month
Dialogue: 3,0:46:54.46,0:46:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，阿贾伊·凯迪亚
Dialogue: 2,0:46:54.46,0:46:55.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But, Ajay Kedia
Dialogue: 3,0:46:56.62,0:46:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你可能认识他
Dialogue: 2,0:46:56.62,0:46:57.66,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You might know him
Dialogue: 3,0:46:58.22,0:47:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他的公司已经预定了
Dialogue: 2,0:46:58.22,0:47:00.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}His company has already booked it
Dialogue: 3,0:47:03.82,0:47:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}多少钱？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:03.82,0:47:04.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How much is it?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:05.34,0:47:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我给你看点别的 -多少钱？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:05.34,0:47:07.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Harshad Bhai, Ill show you something else - How much is it?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:08.82,0:47:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}四百五十万卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:47:08.82,0:47:09.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Its 45 lakhs
Dialogue: 3,0:47:10.62,0:47:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你收预付款了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:10.62,0:47:11.78,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have you taken an advance?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:12.82,0:47:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，我没收，但我已经答应他了，我保证
Dialogue: 2,0:47:12.82,0:47:15.34,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, Ive not taken any But Ive given him My word
Dialogue: 3,0:47:19.82,0:47:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么汽车应该从迪拜直接送到我家
Dialogue: 2,0:47:19.82,0:47:21.42,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then the car should be delivered from Dubai directly to my house
Dialogue: 3,0:47:22.62,0:47:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我给你五百五十万卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:47:22.62,0:47:23.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ill give you 55 lakhs
Dialogue: 3,0:47:25.02,0:47:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}四百五十万买车，一百万买你说的话
Dialogue: 2,0:47:25.02,0:47:26.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Forty-five for the car and ten for your word
Dialogue: 3,0:47:45.02,0:47:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你喜欢这辆车吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:45.02,0:47:45.90,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you like the car?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:47.90,0:47:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很好，但是你要这么多车干什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:47.90,0:47:50.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Its nice But what will you do with so many cars?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:51.50,0:47:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们已经有15到20辆车了
Dialogue: 2,0:47:51.50,0:47:53.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We already have 15 to 20 cars
Dialogue: 3,0:47:54.14,0:47:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:54.14,0:47:55.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Didnt you like it?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:55.06,0:47:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，这很好但是一辆车有什么用呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:55.06,0:47:58.22,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, its good But what good will a car do?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:59.46,0:48:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很多用处
Dialogue: 2,0:47:59.46,0:48:00.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A lot
Dialogue: 3,0:48:01.34,0:48:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}金钱吸引金钱
Dialogue: 2,0:48:01.34,0:48:02.54,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Money attracts money
Dialogue: 3,0:48:03.18,0:48:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们必须知道
Dialogue: 2,0:48:03.18,0:48:04.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}People must know
Dialogue: 3,0:48:04.30,0:48:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}米哈特人不亚于安巴尼人或塔塔人
Dialogue: 2,0:48:04.30,0:48:06.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that the Mehtas are no less than Ambanis or Tatas
