Dialogue: 2,0:48:54.66,0:48:55.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Phone
Dialogue: 3,0:48:55.98,0:48:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 是谁?-他说是从德里来的
Dialogue: 2,0:48:55.98,0:48:58.30,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Whos it? - Says hes from Delhi
Dialogue: 3,0:49:03.02,0:49:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你好?-你好，梅塔先生
Dialogue: 2,0:49:03.02,0:49:04.50,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hello? -[Swami] Greetings, Mehta ji
Dialogue: 3,0:49:04.98,0:49:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是圣斯瓦米，来自德里
Dialogue: 2,0:49:04.98,0:49:06.62,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Its Santswami, from Delhi
Dialogue: 3,0:49:09.22,0:49:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}晚上好，阁下
Dialogue: 2,0:49:09.22,0:49:10.38,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hari Om, Swami ji
Dialogue: 3,0:49:11.90,0:49:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很抱歉在这个时候打扰你
Dialogue: 2,0:49:11.90,0:49:13.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sorry to trouble you at this hour
Dialogue: 3,0:49:14.26,0:49:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}时间不是烦恼
Dialogue: 2,0:49:14.26,0:49:15.58,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The time is not the worry
Dialogue: 3,0:49:15.90,0:49:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}烦恼的是，你已经打过电话了
Dialogue: 2,0:49:15.90,0:49:17.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] The worry is that youve called
Dialogue: 3,0:49:20.06,0:49:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只要我在这里，你就没有理由担心
Dialogue: 2,0:49:20.06,0:49:23.10,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}While Im here, you have no reason to worry
Dialogue: 3,0:49:23.74,0:49:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Swami ]你在选举期间给政党提供的所有帮助
Dialogue: 2,0:49:23.74,0:49:26.26,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Swami] All the help youve extended to the parties during elections
Dialogue: 3,0:49:26.38,0:49:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}受到这里每个人的赞赏
Dialogue: 2,0:49:26.38,0:49:28.02,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Swami]is appreciated by everyone here
Dialogue: 3,0:49:28.50,0:49:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个国家和政府在选举之后可能经历了一些变化
Dialogue: 2,0:49:28.50,0:49:31.82,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The country and the government may have undergone some changes after the elections
Dialogue: 3,0:49:31.94,0:49:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是在德里，每个人都想和你保持同样的关系
Dialogue: 2,0:49:31.94,0:49:35.94,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But in Delhi, everyone would like to maintain the same relations with you
Dialogue: 3,0:49:36.22,0:49:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阁下，我希望有机会为政府服务
Dialogue: 2,0:49:36.22,0:49:39.86,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Swami ji, I would love an opportunity to serve the government
Dialogue: 3,0:49:40.46,0:49:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Swami ]你很快就会有机会的，我们很快就会见面的
Dialogue: 2,0:49:40.46,0:49:43.74,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Swami] You will soon get the opportunity, and we shall meet soon